  "about": {
    "showAtStartup": true,
    "title": "Welcome to the FNSB Roads Plan Interactive Comment Map!",
    "text": "<h2>Help Create a Safer and Better-Connected Road System in the Fairbanks North Star Borough!</h2><br><br>Use this COMMENT MAP to:<br>&emsp;• Share what you like or dislike about roads in your neighborhood and/or other locations in the borough.<br>&emsp;• Learn and share your level of support for what others like or dislike.<br><br><br>This interactive map is open for comment through Monday, September 13th.<br><br>Your responses will contribute to an update of the Fairbanks North Star Borough (FNSB) Comprehensive Roads Plan.<br><a href='https://fnsbroadsplan.com/'>Visit the project website to learn more.</a><br><br>THANK YOU for your time and contributions to the updated FNSB Comprehensive Roads Plan!<br><br><h2>Instructions</h2><br><h3>Get Familiar with the Map:</h3><br>&emsp;• Click drag the map to move around and use the “+” or “-“ buttons to zoom in or out.<br><h3>Check Out and Respond to Others’ Comments:</h3><br>&emsp;• Find a comment you agree with/support? Click the “thumb up”. <br><br>&emsp;• Find a comment you disagree with/do not support? Click the “thumb down”. <br><h3>Submit a New Comment:</h3><br>&emsp;• Select the location for your comment<br><br>&emsp;• Click on that location and write a comment about a safety, connectivity or other issue impacting your local/neighborhood roads<br><h3>Tell Us More:</h3><br>&emsp;• <a href='https://www.surveymonkey.com/r/FNSBRoadsPlan'>Take this short 10-minute survey to:</a><br>&emsp;o RATE the safety and connectivity of your local/neighborhood roads.<br>&emsp;o Share your ideas for the TOP 3 NEEDED CONNECTIONS.<br>&emsp;o Identify examples of “GOOD” or “POOR” quality roads in your neighborhood.<br>",
    "thanks": "Thanks to <a href='https://github.com/bmcbride/building-damage-reporter'>Brian McBride</a> and the great folks at <a href='https://www.fulcrumapp.com'>FulcrumApp</a>.",
    "help": "<a href='/connect/help_video.mp4' target='_mfcvid'>Watch Video To Learn More!</a>"
  },
